OL,5, A call for views on standing charges by
OL,6, energy regulator Ofgem has received a  
OL,7, huge response, reflecting customers'   
OL,8, frustration over the fixed daily fee.  
OL,10,FOfgem said 20,000 people had been in   
OL,11,Ftouch before consultation closes later 
OL,12,Fon Friday.                             
OL,14,FThe regulator had said it wanted to    
OL,15,Fopen up debate over the charges,       
OL,16,Fincluding opinions on how to change the
OL,17,Fsystem.                                
OL,19,FQuestions have also been asked about   
OL,20,Fcustomer service when bills are high.  
